<template>
  <parallax-card> </parallax-card>
</template>

<script>
import ParallaxCard from "@/components/UI/ParallaxCard.vue";

export default {
  inject: ["setCurrentPage"],
  components: { ParallaxCard },
  mounted() {
    this.setCurrentPage(
      "Projects",
      "Project",
      "Here is the showcase of my projects"
    );
  },
};
</script>

<style scoped>
#container-main {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 30px;
}
</style>
